{"tid":2368531,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"民政局政助辭職 與丈夫返新加坡","createTime":"2021-01-16T09:27:22.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-16T09:35:03.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"4f554aef689ec512b86211ca0212848352c9cea9","tid":2368531,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T09:27:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210116/UT6TTP6MJFDDTJOB26DAKDPGWE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210116%2FUT6TTP6MJFDDTJOB26DAKDPGWE%2F&d=urW02bDNsyUCiNuSwPhOyLXqul57XbQM8lVYa5HUNM4%3D&h=33b2ce64\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210116%2FUT6TTP6MJFDDTJOB26DAKDPGWE%2F&h=41d0d4dc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210116/UT6TTP6MJFDDTJOB26DAKDPGWE/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n民政局政助辭職 與丈夫返新加坡<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Rki9L9PUQv3DnmCW45i7KaRhiHw=/667x375/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/ULI4U57FF5GVLMC6PJPV7RFGGA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FRki9L9PUQv3DnmCW45i7KaRhiHw%3D%2F667x375%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FULI4U57FF5GVLMC6PJPV7RFGGA.jpg&h=8aefdc31&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■黎穎瑜（右）2017年起出任民政局政助，左為時任局長劉江華。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】特首林鄭月娥班子有人跳船。在政府任職七年多，現年44歲的民政事務局長政治助理黎穎瑜突然辭職。<br />\n<br />\n特區政府昨發出新聞稿，證實黎穎瑜已經請辭，指其請辭原因是「需要照顧家人」。黎穎瑜則於個人社交網站發帖指離任後會與丈夫返新加坡。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n曾任齊心基金會要職<br />\n<br />\n黎穎瑜現正休假，下周三（20日）正式離任。她在社交網站指，其丈夫於新。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n早於梁振英執政年代的2013年，。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n黎穎瑜是現屆政府第二名辭職的政。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"f70fc25923ed37a84e51b1605cafd0ce9d50ec88","tid":2368531,"uid":216664,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T09:27:43.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"large\">-2019 年秋，武漢病毒實驗室 (WIV) 有職員染病，病徵描述與其後12月爆發的肺炎疫情相近<br />\n-2003 年沙士疫情後，武漢病毒實驗室 (WIV) 成為了世界知名的冠狀病毒研究中心<br />\n-至少從 2016 年起，武漢病毒實驗室 (WIV) 開始對RaTG13蝙蝠冠狀病毒進行實驗，此病毒與 Covid-19 96.2% 相近</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZZATAr7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZZATAr7.png&h=ad4e7407&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國國務院官方調查：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.state.gov/fact-sheet-activity-at-the-wuhan-institute-of-virology/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.state.gov%2Ffact-sheet-activity-at-the-wuhan-institute-of-virology%2F&d=urW02bDNsyUCiNuSwPhOyLXqul57XbQM8lVYa5HUNM4%3D&h=c647797e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.state.gov/fact-sheet-activity-at-the-wuhan-institute-of-virology/</a>"},{"pid":"969d9aeca2cbd33df0a5fa16623a1d45760a9f82","tid":2368531,"uid":334957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T09:29:50.000Z","msg":"Go back to monkeypore"},{"pid":"b92c13ae0d45d29843e5775cd47ece97332c9af9","tid":2368531,"uid":282637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T09:35:03.000Z","msg":"有國才有家,丈夫仲親過黨?賣國賊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}